# Skill Parser Review
Name: parser-review
Summary:
    Review a parser change and produce concrete findings.

## Triggers
- Trigger:
    Phrase: review this parser
    Intent: code-review
- Trigger:
    Phrase: inspect mol fixtures
    Intent: test-review

## Workflow
Step:
    Name: Gather context
    Output: Understand the changed files and tests
Step:
    Name: Find risks
    Output: Focus on regressions and missing coverage

## Constraints

Prefer findings over summaries.
Keep comments concise.
Use file references when possible.
